#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:84
msgid "End Portal"
msgstr "エンドポータル"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:85
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:362
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:389
msgid "Used to construct end portals"
msgstr "エンドポータルの構築に使用"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:86
msgid ""
"An End portal teleports creatures and objects to the mysterious End "
"dimension (and back!)."
msgstr ""
"エンドポータルは、生物や物を不可思議なエンドの次元にテレポートさせます（また"
"戻ってくる事も可能）。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:87
msgid ""
"Hop into the portal to teleport. Entering an End portal in the Overworld "
"teleports you to a fixed position in the End dimension and creates a 5×5 "
"obsidian platform at your destination. End portals in the End will lead back "
"to your spawn point in the Overworld."
msgstr ""
"ポータルに飛び込むとテレポート。（オーバーワールドにあるエンドポータルに入る"
"と、エンド次元の固定位置にテレポートし、目的地に5×5の黒曜石のプラットフォーム"
"が作成されます。そのエンドポータルに入れば、オーバーワールドのスポーン地点に"
"戻れます）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:308
msgid "Leaving the End"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:316
msgid "Entering the End"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:361
msgid "End Portal Frame"
msgstr "エンドポータル・フレーム"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:363
msgid ""
"End portal frames are used in the construction of End portals. Each block "
"has a socket for an eye of ender."
msgstr ""
"エンドポータル・フレームは、エンダーアイを入れるソケットがあり、エンドポータ"
"ルの構築に使われます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:363
msgid ""
"NOTE: The End dimension is currently incomplete and might change in future "
"versions."
msgstr ""
"注：エンド次元は現在未完成であり、将来のバージョンで変更される可能性がありま"
"す。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:364
msgid ""
"To create an End portal, you need 12 end portal frames and 12 eyes of ender. "
"The end portal frames have to be arranged around a horizontal 3×3 area with "
"each block facing inward. Any other arrangement will fail."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:364
msgid ""
"Place an eye of ender into each block. The end portal appears in the middle "
"after placing the final eye."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:364
msgid "Once placed, an eye of ender can not be taken back."
msgstr "エンダーアイは、一度置くと取り戻せません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_end.lua:388
msgid "End Portal Frame with Eye of Ender"
msgstr "エンドポータル・フレーム（エンダーアイ入り）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_gateway.lua:45
msgid "End Gateway Portal"
msgstr "エンドゲートウェイポータル"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_gateway.lua:46
msgid "Used to construct end gateway portals"
msgstr "エンドゲートウェイポータルの構築に使用"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_gateway.lua:47
msgid ""
"An End gateway portal teleports creatures and objects to the outer End (and "
"back!)."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_gateway.lua:48
msgid ""
"Throw an ender pearl into the portal to teleport. Entering an Gateway portal "
"near the Overworld teleports you to the outer End. At this destination "
"another gateway portal will be constructed, which you can use to get back."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:597
msgid "Entering the Nether"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:598
msgid "Leaving the Nether"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:675
msgid "Obsidian is also used as the frame of Nether portals."
msgstr "黒曜石は、ネザーポータルの枠組としても使われます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:676
msgid ""
"To open a Nether portal, place an upright frame of obsidian with a width of "
"at least 4 blocks and a height of 5 blocks, leaving only air in the center. "
"After placing this frame, light a fire in the obsidian frame. Nether portals "
"only work in the Overworld and the Nether."
msgstr ""
"ネザーポータルを開くには、まず黒曜石で直立した枠組を構築します（幅4ブロック以"
"上、高さ5ブロック以上。内側は中空にして黒曜石を配置）。その後、枠の中に火をつ"
"けます。ネザーポータルは、オーバーワールドとネザーでしか使えません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:742
msgid "Nether Portal"
msgstr "ネザーポータル"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:743
msgid ""
"A Nether portal teleports creatures and objects to the hot and dangerous "
"Nether dimension (and back!). Enter at your own risk!"
msgstr ""
"ネザーポータルは、生物や物を熱くて危険なネザー次元にテレポートさせます（また"
"戻ってくる事も可能）。入るのは自己責任で！"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:744
msgid ""
"Stand in the portal for a moment to activate the teleportation. Entering a "
"Nether portal for the first time will also create a new portal in the other "
"dimension. If a Nether portal has been built in the Nether, it will lead to "
"the Overworld. A Nether portal is destroyed if the any of the obsidian which "
"surrounds it is destroyed, or if it was caught in an explosion."
msgstr ""
"ポータルの中でしばらく立っていると、テレポートが有効になります。初めて入った"
"時は、異次元の方にも新たなポータルが作られます（それはオーバーワールドに通じ"
"ています）。ネザーポータルは、それを囲む黒曜石のどれかが破壊されたり、爆発に"
"巻き込まれたりすると壊れます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_portals/portal_nether.lua:799
msgid "Dump coordinates of registered portals"
msgstr ""

